    <abstract>
      <t>BGP link bandwidth extended community provides a way to signal a value along with a BGP path that can be used to perform weighted load-balancing in multipath scenarios. This document details various use cases of the BGP link bandwidth extended community. It also describes local mechanisms to dynamically adjust the BGP link bandwidth value or the multipath weights based on different considerations.</t>
